name: Lebron X 'Championship' Pack
description:
Lebron X 'Championship' Pack

The pack consists of the two limited edition LeBron X kicks. The first is the red, black and gold PS ELITE version worn by King James in Game 1 of the Finals series and features a glossy red upper with subtle geometric palm-leaf graphics, a speckled midsole and gold Swoosh designs. The sock-liners are imprinted with “2-time champion” on the left and “11-12, 12-13″ on the right. The Air Max LeBron X Low boasts a unique floral palm splatter print along with matte black accents and a glow-in-the-dark outsole. The shoes are packaged in a special double box, of course in championship gold, as well as two black and gold commemorative LeBron X shoe bags.
